“Mida Click to Call” extension for Google Chrome allows to quickly call numbers found on web pages, just clicking on them with the right button of the mouse. The call is then managed by Mida Attendant Console Pro. 

 

Please note that “Mida Click to Call” extension is not required for Mida Attendant Console Pro to function. It is an optional extension and its lacking doesn’t interfere with the correct functioning of Mida Attendant Console Pro.
